Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.81,0:00:05.98,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:2815,5985}A Wonderful Rival!\NAsuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:12.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:11115,12700}Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:14.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:12700,14452}Let's walk home together!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:15.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:14452,15245}Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:17.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:16162,17413}We heard the news!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:22.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:17413,22585}You've been asked by the Mayor to help\Narrest that phantom thief, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.92,0:00:25.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:23920,25088}Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:26.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:25088,26256}Yup, it sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:27.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:26256,27924}Wow! That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:30.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:27924,30301}They say you did great\Non the last case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.05,0:00:34.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:31052,34847}How you protected the\Njewels from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:37.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:34847,37809}It was all over the papers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:39.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:37809,39269}I read that article, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:42.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:39769,42397}It said, "He protected the Blue\NMeteorite from St. Tail
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:44.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:42397,44440}and helped in the arrest of Umido".\NThat's how it went?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:45.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:44440,45984}Yup, that's how it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:49.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:46693,49904}But you let St. Tail get away,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:53.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:50655,53241}That's why I've been\Nasked to catch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:57.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:53741,57579}I'm the only one who's\Nseen her up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:01.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:59289,61541}See! This is my official permit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:03.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:61874,63001}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:06.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:63751,66504}It's the badge I got from the Mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:10.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:67255,70967}All I have to do is show this\Nand I can get in to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:13.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:71384,73428}Hey, that's really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:16.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:73428,76931}Does your dad know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:20.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:77640,80560}He got himself all worked up over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:22.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:80560,82562}He wants me to get\Nthe job done, do or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:27.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:83771,87400}Isn't that St. Tail's first failure?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.81,0:01:28.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:87817,88943}{\an8\i1}"Failure"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:31.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:88234,91195}And her nemesis is Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:33.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:91195,93615}I've got to hand it to you,\Nyou're great!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:34.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93615,94866}It's true, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:36.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:94866,96701}Ain't it fabulous?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:38.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:96701,98995}Ah, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:40.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:98995,100121}You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:41.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100121,101414}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:43.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:101414,103541}I haven't failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:46.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:104375,106336}Whose voice was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:47.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106336,107503}Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:52.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:109631,112925}Oh, Meimi, don't let it bother you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:55.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:112925,115511}I've never failed once!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:56.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:115720,116804}I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:59.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116804,119641}Why don't you drop by the\Nchurch for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:02.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119641,122477}I haven't failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:08.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126773,128900}He's really asking for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:11.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:128900,131944}As if a guy like that could catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:14.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131944,134781}My, you're fired up,\Naren't you Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:16.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134781,136407}That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:18.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136824,138576}Your mission this time is…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:24.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143289,144874}This tiara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:27.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145500,147669}It's called Electra.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:28.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147669,148920}Electra?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:35.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152215,155218}Named for the star\Nin the Subaru constellation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:37.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155218,157053}Also known as "the missing one".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:43.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158137,163017}It was stolen from someone by Egami,\Nwho lives on 7th avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:47.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163643,167980}Let's return it to its rightful owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:49.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168564,169816}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:50.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169816,170483}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:52.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170817,172527}This wouldn't be a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:54.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172527,174362}You heard, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:58.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174362,178491}Asuka Jr. received a badge from the\NMayor, granting investigation power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:00.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178491,180493}He's all wound up\Nand ready to leap into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:05.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181536,185707}Meimi, you're not afraid of\NAsuka Jr., are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:06.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185707,186416}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:10.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187875,190503}If that's so, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:13.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190503,193047}Let's forget about this caper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:14.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193047,194507}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:15.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194507,195717}You're kidding, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:17.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196134,197802}Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197802,200346}You just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:27.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202098,207103}I'm not afraid of a bumbling\Ndetective like him at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:31.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209021,211065}I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:37.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214235,217071}St. Tail… Isn't she wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:40.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217739,220783}She's exactly like me\Nwhen I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:41.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220783,221534}Aww shoot…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:44.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222744,224036}That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227206,228750}What's the matter, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229417,231294}The balloons…\Nwhere have I put them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:53.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232170,233337}Balloons?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:55.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233337,235089}The ones I use for my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:00.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237008,240261}Aren't they supposed to\Nbe in your trunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:03.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240261,243306}Yes, but they're not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:09.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247518,249937}Only the balloons have disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:12.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250104,252648}Papa, are you sure they're missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:15.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254150,255902}Remember what happened\Nthe other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256444,258905}You put two socks on one foot
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:21.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258905,261574}and went around saying\N"Where's my other sock?!".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:23.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261574,263367}Oh, don't bring that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:27.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265953,267330}Anyway, it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:40.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279801,280843}Hey! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:42.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280843,282220}Asuka! Up in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:43.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282220,283304}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:47.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286641,287809}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:52.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288059,292772}{\i1}"I'll be picking up the Electra\Ntonight – St. Tail."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:55.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293314,295775}It's a note from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:58.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295983,298778}Hey, it's a challenge! What class!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:01.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300196,301239}You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:02.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301239,302281}This is fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:04.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302949,304367}She's the phantom, alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:05.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304367,305827}She's got real guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:12.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310164,312792}I'll be ready for you, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:20.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316546,320758}Meimi? Just what is this\Nall about exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:27.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322677,327557}Hey have you heard? St. Tail\Nsent Asuka Jr. a challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:28.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327557,328975}Don't you think that's strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328975,330726}What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:35.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331477,335815}Why do you think\Nshe told Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:38.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335815,338150}It does seem too good to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:39.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:338150,339193}Doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:45.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342530,345324}Maybe St. Tail and Asuka Jr. are…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345324,346868}No doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:49.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346868,349620}The two of them\Nare in this together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353708,355626}So…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:06:00.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357128,360590}St. Tail has sent a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:04.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360590,364343}I won't let anyone get\Nmy tiara, Electra!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:10.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366220,370433}Sir, there is a rumor going around…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370433,371809}Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:17.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373352,377523}What! St. Tail and Asuka Jr.\Nare working together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:18.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377523,378608}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:26.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382695,386032}You're Mr. Egami, the tiara's owner,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:27.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386032,387158}And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:32.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388075,392038}The Mayor asked me to assist in\Nthe St. Tail investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:33.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392038,393831}My name is Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:34.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394123,394832}Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:38.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395416,398794}Oh, so you're Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399253,400796}I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:46.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404717,406177}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:54.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411599,414435}I leave all security in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:56.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414435,416228}Yes, sir! I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:58.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416228,418230}Please catch St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:01.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419148,421943}No matter what\Nthe rumors may say…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:04.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421943,424195}I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:07.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425529,427657}Rumors?\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428282,429784}You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:13.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429784,433663}There's great doubt\Nabout you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:19.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434497,439585}It's suspected that you\Nare St. Tail's accomplice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440044,441587}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:25.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442463,445633}She sent you a note, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:27.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445633,447009}Wait, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:28.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447009,448052}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:32.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448052,452515}I'm sure it's all just rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:38.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453432,458938}For the sake of clearing your name,\Nplease protect my Electra.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458938,460356}Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:42.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460773,462942}Who'd want to work with\Nthat girl, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:44.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463484,464485}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:49.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466195,469198}Everything is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:51.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469198,471909}The tiara is in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:54.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472535,474620}Everything has gone well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:58.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475663,478874}The fool trusted me completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:03.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480126,483254}I'd never be tricked\Nby a brat like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:07.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485131,487800}I'll set them both up and turn him in\Nto the police along with St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:11.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489677,491762}By the way, Mr. Egami,\Nwhere is Electra right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:16.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492930,496475}The truth is, hearing about the\Nchallenge made me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:20.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496475,500730}I couldn't leave it in the mansion,\Nso I've hidden it in a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:24.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501355,504150}You're really a worrier, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504150,506694}So, where did you hide it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508029,509405}Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:39.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516579,519081}At the top of that clock tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:45.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521667,525296}Why hide it in such a difficult place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:46.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525296,526589}Where exactly in the\Nclock tower is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527131,528966}On the face of the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528966,530551}Behind the hour hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:00.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540019,540811}What!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:03.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540811,543355}On the face of the clock,\Nbehind the hour hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:07.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544857,547485}That's a tough place to get it from.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:11.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547735,551947}Actually, I know for sure he's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:13.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551947,553449}The tiara is really behind\Nthe minute hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:17.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554825,557828}How did you get\Ninformation like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:22.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558287,562124}Egami is trying to frame Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562416,564126}What? A trap!
Comment: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:29.59,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:569590,569590}Eyecatch A
Comment: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:35.59,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:575596,575596}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:40.60,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:580601,580601}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:51.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587274,591737}There's a rumor that Asuka Jr.\Nis St. Tail's accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:56.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591737,596158}Egami would never tell him the true\Nhiding place of the tiara, would he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:05.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598869,605167}He lied so Asuka Jr. will be\Narrested along with St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:07.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605543,607253}That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:10.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607253,610673}It's all because of that note you sent\Nto challenge him, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:12.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611423,612633}You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:17.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613592,617513}I guess so… He's getting set up,\Nbecause of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:27.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619723,627481}If you steal the tiara from the minute\Nhand, Asuka Jr.'s name is cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:29.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627940,629316}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:33.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630151,633445}My lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:39.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638450,639451}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:43.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641871,643122}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:46.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645291,646792}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:04.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661390,664351}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:08.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666687,668647}But I'll tell you this…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:12.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668647,672067}I'm not doing this to help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:13.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672067,673235}Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:15.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673986,675946}Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:34.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693380,694465}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:38.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695758,698135}Do you intend to sit there and\Nstake out the place all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698928,701096}Not all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:44.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701096,704099}St. Tail will be coming\Nat exactly 6:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:47.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705684,707269}How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:51.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707269,711023}The only time St. Tail can reach\Nthe hour hand is 6:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:55.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711982,715277}To steal Electra at any other time…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:57.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716403,717488}…is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:59.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718072,719365}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:02.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719365,722076}I'm counting on you, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:05.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724411,725955}I'm waiting for you, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:14.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728666,734046}What a fool! You don't know that\NElectra is behind the minute hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:17.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734421,737925}At 6:00, everyone will see\Nthat you and St. Tail
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737925,739385}are both idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:44.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762992,764994}Looks like there isn't any security.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:49.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767329,769999}I have to climb the clock tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784138,785097}That's…!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:18.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793647,798027}Almost 6:00. Time for St. Tail\Nto make her appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:20.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799278,800821}Sir! We've got trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:23.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800821,803490}What's wrong?\NWhy are you so excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:28.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:803991,808454}Sir! Someone is climbing the ladder\Non the side of the clock tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:29.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808746,809580}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:32.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809580,812791}That ladder leads to the top stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:33.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812791,813542}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:59.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836607,839693}Okay! St. Tail, come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:01.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839693,841153}Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:03.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842112,843155}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:07.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843155,847409}What a beautiful moon.\NI'm so happy you waited for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847701,849411}St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:11.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849912,851205}Why are you up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:13.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851580,853457}I know where it's really hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:16.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853457,856877}Electra is behind the minute hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:19.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858504,859880}Behind the minute hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:32.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869515,872976}Well, that's it. I've got Electra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:39.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877689,879650}My Electra is being stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:42.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879650,882236}Wait! St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882236,883695}Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885030,886990}What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:49.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886990,889451}Mr. Egami, you said the Electra was\Nbehind the hour hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:50.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889451,890744}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:53.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891120,893705}St. Tail, I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899169,900629}You can't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:03.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900963,903632}Don't move, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:10.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907094,910139}It's showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:27.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923694,927197}That's the balloon she used\Nto send me the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927823,929700}Bye, bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:31.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930200,931702}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:33.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932161,933662}You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:52.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950888,952306}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:59.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956768,959271}This time, I'll bust that big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:03.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960564,963108}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:04.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963108,964359}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980918,982628}This will get my Electra back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988050,989885}You brat! How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:46.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004483,1006818}Cut it out! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:52.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011114,1012699}Stop… please…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:03.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019831,1023210}I wasn't trying to protect you!\NDon't misunderstand what I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:08.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027631,1028549}Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:10.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028549,1030175}Keep sending me those challenges!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:12.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030634,1032177}Give me a fair chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:14.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032594,1034721}I'll get you sooner or later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:17.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034721,1037140}Are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:26.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042604,1046275}{\i1}I don't know why,\Nbut it's fun to have him around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:30.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046275,1050112}{\i1}And I'll do anything\Nto keep on feeling this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:39.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057744,1059121}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059121,1060581}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:52.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069631,1072467}The real owner was very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:55.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072467,1075053}She says, "Thank you for\Nreturning Electra".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:58.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075887,1078265}Hang on a sec.\NI'll catch up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078265,1079308}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:05.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082311,1085022}That old man…\Nhe even had me fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:07.48,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1085022,1087482}Egami Arrested!\NSaint Tail Strikes Again
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:07.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085856,1087482}Hey, great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:09.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087899,1089901}You're a hero in the papers, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:11.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089901,1091612}You caught another crook, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:15.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091612,1095282}Yeah… but St. Tail still got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:18.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095282,1098952}Well, you can give us\Nthe details later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:21.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100162,1101455}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:23.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102456,1103999}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:26.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105250,1106877}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:29.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106877,1109880}Glad to hear your name's been cleared.\NThat's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109880,1111548}Yeah. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:37.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113008,1117346}And you let St. Tail get away again.\NI hear you're on bad terms with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:40.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117929,1120223}What do you mean, "again"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:43.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120223,1123810}Anyway, it's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:47.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125020,1127814}Ah, she's a hopeless case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:51.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129775,1131818}But that cut…! Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:01.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139117,1141495}Well, hang in there till next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:07.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143455,1147751}I know that St. Tail is a girl\Nabout the same age as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:10.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149336,1150712}It couldn't be…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:13.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151797,1153173}Nah, it can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:34.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168230,1174236}St. Tail Mini-Theatre!\N"The Great Hot Potato Chase!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:45.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181284,1185914}Autumn leaves.\NIt'll be fall in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:48.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187165,1188041}Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:50.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188041,1190877}I'm at the best part of the story,\Nso don't talk to me right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:53.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190877,1193630}Autumn, is a season for reading…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:56.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193630,1196675}But how about reading something\Nother than comic books sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:20:00.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197843,1200804}Ah… "Autumn of Romance."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:03.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200804,1203348}I'd like to be chased by
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:07.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203348,1207519}a handsome, passionate lover,\Nlike the girl in this comic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:15.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207519,1215736}But Meimi, you do have a passionate\Nperson chasing after you, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:22.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217779,1222367}{\an8}Hot potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:29.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227164,1229624}Meimi! How unladylike!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:33.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229624,1233420}My, Seira.\NWasn't that your stomach just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:42.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234796,1242637}{\an8}That's right, ladies! Come and get them!\NThey're hot and sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:46.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243096,1246641}Autumn's the season to\Ncrave sweet potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:50.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247476,1250645}{\an8}Stone-baked sweet potatoes!\NHot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:53.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251104,1253482}Well then Meimi, please go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:59.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253482,1259362}Hey, just a minute!\NWhy should I have to go buy it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:05.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259905,1265076}I'm a servant of God. Sister told me\Nit's forbidden for me to buy and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:08.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1265285,1268580}Oh really? Then that means I don't\Nhave to get one for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:16.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269456,1276797}Buying is forbidden, but it's fine\Nto have a kind friend share a snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:21.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278757,1281051}I always have to play these roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:23.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281051,1283720}Someday,\NSeira's gonna get punished!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:28.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1283887,1288099}{\an8}Natural and delicious!\NStone-baked hot potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:29.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287140,1289601}Nobody's looking… here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:31.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289601,1291144}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:33.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1291144,1293855}Hey! Haneoka, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:36.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294856,1296691}That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:39.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297859,1299194}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:41.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299611,1301696}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:44.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301988,1304699}Wha… what?\NIt's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:47.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1305200,1307869}What about you!\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:49.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1307869,1309246}What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:52.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309246,1312374}I'm in the middle of an investigation\Nto catch St. Tail's tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:56.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312374,1316545}Don't even try. St. Tail isn't\Na slowpoke that you'd be able to catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:57.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316545,1317754}What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:22:01.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1317754,1321800}The Mayor himself\Ncommissioned me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:03.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322384,1323885}So don't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:06.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324803,1326221}Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:07.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326221,1327514}This isn't a Samurai movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:10.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327514,1330225}Who'd be impressed with\Na thing like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:11.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330225,1331852}– What did you say?!\N– What of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:15.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331852,1335564}{\an8}Stone-baked hot potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.94,0:22:18.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1336940,1338608}{\an8}Piping hot sweet potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:21.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1338608,1341528}Wait! Mr. hot potato vendor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:24.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1343363,1344531}What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:28.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1345407,1348827}Why are you acting so strange?\NDid you want to buy a sweet potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:32.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1349202,1352247}That's right! Anything wrong with that?!\NGo ahead and laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:35.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1352247,1355750}How stupid.\NThat's nothing to be ashamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.75,0:22:37.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1355750,1357961}I like them, too.\NSweet potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:40.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1359045,1360547}Get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.08,0:22:43.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1361089,1363550}Let's go!\NWe can still catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.55,0:22:54.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1372559,1374311}All right!\NThere it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:09.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1387407,1389492}It's a patrol car!\NWhat are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:12.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1389492,1392329}We can't stop!\NWhat am I supposed to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:15.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1392787,1395582}You two on the bicycle up ahead!\NStop right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:19.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1396166,1399210}Oh, no!\NIt's my dad's patrol car!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.66,0:23:23.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1399669,1403423}Blah blah blah blah…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.54,0:23:26.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1404549,1406217}I'm sorry Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:27.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1406217,1407636}It's all because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:29.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1407636,1409179}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.17,0:23:31.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1409179,1411514}I'm used to Dad chewing me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:35.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1411973,1415268}More importantly, I'm sorry we\Ndidn't get to buy the sweet potato.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.26,0:23:38.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1416269,1418438}Oh yeah! I forgot all about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:40.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1418438,1420482}What do you mean you forgot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:45.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1420482,1425195}{\an8}Piping hot sweet potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.19,0:23:48.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1427197,1428573}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.57,0:23:50.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1428573,1430867}Sweet potato vendor!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.83,0:24:01.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1438833,1441461}Meimi sure is taking a long time!
