Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.39,0:27:47.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1663391,1667228}There's a super cute hedgehog\Nin a pet shop nearby.{NOTE:めちゃくちゃ可愛いハリネズミちゃんが近所のペットショップにいるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.22,0:27:50.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1667228,1670064}I want it as a pet.\NI go to the store nearly every day!{NOTE:私、ペットにしたくて毎日通ってたんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.06,0:27:55.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1670064,1675820}What? Bad people plan to use\Npoor hedgehog to steal some diamonds?{NOTE:ところがダイヤに目が眩んだ人が、ハリネズミちゃんを利用して悪い事をしようと企んでたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.82,0:27:57.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1675820,1677614}I won't let them!{NOTE:もう絶対許せない}
